# Cloudflare Static Executive Presence Platform

This file is the canonical operating contract for `imagencoach.com`.

It governs content, routing, static publishing, SEO, GEO, AI retrieval, Cloudflare deployment, UI structure and agent behavior. If another repository document conflicts with this file, this file wins.

## Core Mission

Transform ImagenCoach.com into the highest authority holistic executive image coaching platform in Mexico and LATAM.

The platform must dominate:

- Google SERPs
- GEO retrieval
- AI search engines
- executive buyer intent
- leadership positioning searches
- image coaching semantic categories

while preserving Sonia's:

- emotional sophistication
- psychological depth
- coaching philosophy
- human warmth
- holistic methodology

## Primary Brand Positioning

Imagen Coach is not:

- fashion consulting
- wellness coaching
