## UI System

Design principle:

```text
Calmado
Elegante
Espacioso
Editorial
Premium
Humano
Ejecutivo
```

Mandatory spacing:

```text
8px spacing grid
```

Allowed scale:

```text
8
16
24
32
48
64
96
128
```

Required breakpoints:

```text
320
480
768
1024
1280
1440
```

Mobile rules:

- no text walls
- no oversized hero blocks
- no CLS jumps
- no uneven spacing
- no oversized padding
- no inconsistent card alignment

## Image Rules

All images:

- AVIF or WebP where practical
- lazy loaded when below the fold
- width and height defined
- compressed
- responsive

Bad alt/filename:

```text
image1.webp
```

Good alt/filename:

```text
sonia-mcrorey-coaching-imagen-presencia-profesional.webp
```

## Performance Rules

Hard targets:

- LCP under 1.8s
- CLS under 0.05
- TTFB under 200ms
- minimal JS
- static rendering

## Cloudflare Rules

Enable:

- HTTP/3
- Brotli
- Early Hints
- Tiered Cache
- Auto Minify
- Image Optimization
- Smart Compression

## AGENTS.md Directive

The agent must optimize for:

- executive buyer intent
